# Cover Letter - Account Executive at Revolut

## Dear Hiring Manager,

With over **20 years of experience in investing, banking, and financial strategy**, I am excited to apply for the **Account Executive** position at Revolut. As a seasoned finance professional with a background in **economics, multilingual proficiency (German native, fluent in English, Italian, and Spanish), and a strong track record in sales and client engagement**, I am confident that my expertise aligns perfectly with this role.

Having worked in **two banks and across investment markets**, I have developed a deep understanding of **financial products, SaaS-driven solutions, and client acquisition strategies**. My ability to **build and manage key client relationships, conduct persuasive financial sales pitches, and navigate complex investment landscapes** allows me to excel in high-stakes sales environments.

## Key qualifications that make me a strong fit for this role:

✔ **Extensive Sales & Investment Expertise** – Proven success in presentations and driving revenue growth in competitive financial markets.  
✔ **Strategic Prospecting & Business Development** – Experienced in identifying and engaging key prospects across multiple industries, leveraging a solution-oriented sales approach to maximize client acquisition and retention.  
✔ **C-Level Negotiation & Relationship Management** – Skilled in conducting high-impact sales pitches and advisory meetings with senior executives, ensuring alignment between financial solutions and customer needs.  
✔ **Multilingual & International Sales Experience** – With **German as my native language and fluency in English, Italian, and Spanish**, I effectively communicate with diverse client bases across European markets, building trust and fostering long-term partnerships.  

Revolut’s mission to **redefine financial services** resonates strongly with my passion for **digital innovation and investment solutions**. I am eager to contribute my **sales expertise, financial acumen, and entrepreneurial mindset** to help expand Revolut’s customer base and accelerate its growth.

I would welcome the opportunity to further discuss how my experience can add value to your team.

**Best regards,**  
Severin Grussmann
